\id PRO Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h OLCUEIH
\toc1 OLCUEIH
\toc2 Olcueih
\toc3 Olc
\mt1 OLCUEIH
\mt2 (Proverbs)
\is1 Olcueih Cabu Kawng
\im Olcueih cabu he Thuituen Ol \tl (Ecclesiate)\tl* neh Joba \tl (Job)\tl* cabu bangla Jews rhoek kah olcueih ol pakhat la om. He cabu dongah Pathen loh lunglai a longim neh tlueptluep a suennah kawng, Pathen kah mangtaengnah neh hlanghing a bomnah kawng a tael. Israel ca rhoek kah olcueih aka om te boeih a coi tih tun a khueh. He kah dongah he pilnam kah khosaknah, khoboe rhamlang, omih kawng, mawtnah, imkhui sadingnah kawng, pilnam kah khosaknah kawng a thui. Cueinah a kung la Pathen om tih boethae halangnah a then pawt kawng te a thui. He boeih nen ni Pathen hinyahnah kawng a tueng thai a ti. Boethae halang loh hlang he pocinah lamni a mawt. Cueihnah loh Pathen taengah uepom la om tih, Boeipa hnukbang ham khaw a hoihaeng.
\iot Outline
\io1 I. Solomon kah Olcueih \ior 1. 1—9. 18\ior*
